oinjava.com\/log4j2\/log4j2-consoleappender-example\/\">Log4j2 ConsoleAppender<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/howtodoinjava.com\/log4j2\/log4j2-rollingfileappender-example\/\">Log4j2 RollingFileAppender<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/howtodoinjava.com\/log4j2\/levelrangefilter-example\/\">Log4j2 LevelRangeFilter<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/howtodoinjava.com\/log4j2\/xml-layout\/\">Log4j2 XMLLayout<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/howtodoinjava.com\/log4j2\/log4j2-htmllayout-configuration-example\/\">Log4j2 HTMLLayout<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/howtodoinjava.com\/log4j2\/multiple-appenders\/\">Log4j2 Multiple Appenders<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>1.3. Advance Topics<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/howtodoinjava.com\/logback\/logging-with-mapped-diagnostic-context\/\">Java Logging with Mapped Diagnostic Context (MDC)<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/howtodoinjava.com\/log4j2\/threadcontext-fish-tagging\/\">Log4j2 ThreadContext \u2013 Fish Tagging<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/howtodoinjava.com\/log4j2\/useful-conversion-pattern-examples\/\">Log4j2 \u2013 Useful Log Format Pattern Layouts<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/howtodoinjava.com\/log4j2\/configure-log4j2-for-junit\/\">Configure Log4j2 for JUnit Tests<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/howtodoinjava.com\/log4j2\/slf4j-vs-log4j-which-one-is-better\/\">SLF4j Vs Log4j \u2013 Which One is Better?<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/howtodoinjava.com\/log4j2\/reload-log4j-on-runtime\/\">Reloading Log4j2 Configuration<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>2. Logback<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3>2.1. Basics, Appenders and Layouts<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/howtodoinjava.com\/logback\/logback-tutorial\/\">Logback Tutorial<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/howtodoinjava.com\/logback\/logback-console-appender\/\">Logback Console Appender<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/howtodoinjava.com\/logback\/rollingfileappender\/\">Logback RollingFileAppender<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/howtodoinjava